RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2008-2047. State v. Palmer.

Hamilton App. No. C-010583, 178 Ohio App.3d 192, 2008-Ohio-4604. Reported at 124 Ohio St.3d 282, 2010-Ohio-224, 921 N.E.2d 649. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent and would grant the motion and hold the cause for the decision in 2009-0897, State v. Fischer, Summit App. No. 24406, 2009-Ohio-1491.
